He is famous for taking part in the first successful circumnavigation via both the geographical poles, completed with Charles Burton in 1982.

Fiennes also achieved a world first in 1992-1993 by completing the first unsupported crossing of the Antarctic Continent with Mike Stroud in what was the longest unsupported polar journey in history.

He also successfully reached the summit 
